                            <comment id="35142" author="luke" created="Fri, 25 Apr 2008 08:59:41 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;This looks like a duplicate of &lt;a href=&quot;https://jira.spring.io/browse/SEC-656&quot; title=&quot;exceptionMappings in ProviderManager should be configurable&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;SEC-656&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;SEC-656&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt;. &lt;/p&gt;

